gas and petrochemical processing industries through continuous innovation hudson became the pioneer in this field developing internationallyrecognized trademarks such as finfan® aircooled heat exchangers hyfin® extruded finned tubing and tuflite® and tuflite ii® frp axial flow fans for air coolers cooling towers condensers chillers and hvac applications hudsons premier products and reputation for supplying the highest quality reliability and service in the industry has resulted in an installed base of over  aircooled heat exchangers and  fans throughout the world about riverstone holdings llc riverstone an energy and powerfocused private equity firm founded by pierre f lapeyre and david m leuschen in  has approximately  billion under management across six investment funds riverstone conducts buyout and growth capital investments in the midstream exploration  production oilfield service power and renewable sectors of the energy industry with offices in new york london and houston the firm has committed approximately  billion to more than  investments in north america latin america europe and asia for more information visit wwwriverstonellccom contacts for riverstone holdingskekst and companyjeffrey taufield  michael freitag  contacts for riverstone holdingskekst and companyjeffrey taufield  michael freitag  search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up riverstone holdings llc  riverstone energy limited riverstone energy limited cookie policy our website uses cookies to distinguish you from other users of our website by continuing to use our site you agree to our use of cookies find out more home about the board portfolio news  media investors contact riverstone holdings llc about strategy riverstone holdings llc the investment manager is an affiliate of riverstone holdings llc riverstone riverstone is an energy and powerfocused private investment firm founded in  by david m leuschen and pierre lapeyre jr with approximately  billion of equity capital